      <title>中国暴力事件频发 引发经济焦虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/china-s-spate-of-violence-prompts-outburst-of-economic-anxiety</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国社交媒体用户对近期一系列暴力袭击事件的反应，暴露出人们对国家经济下滑和经济压力加大普遍的不满情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/china-s-spate-of-violence-prompts-outburst-of-economic-anxiety</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 01:56:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保罗·佩洛西的袭击者也被州法院判处绑架罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-21/urgent-attacker-of-nancy-pelosi-s-husband-also-found-guilty-of-kidnapping-and-could-face-more-prison-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山（美联社）——一名男子因袭击前众议院议长南希·佩洛西的丈夫而被判处 30 年联邦监禁，周五他被裁定加重绑架罪名成立，该罪名将被判处终身监禁，不得假释。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-21/urgent-attacker-of-nancy-pelosi-s-husband-also-found-guilty-of-kidnapping-and-could-face-more-prison-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 23:19:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
