      <title>加拿大对华电动汽车关税计划引发最佳方案争论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/canada-s-china-ev-tariff-plan-draws-debate-over-best-approach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府考虑征收关税以保护国内产业之际，汽车和环保组织对加拿大应在多大程度上对中国制造的电动汽车征收新关税存在分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/canada-s-china-ev-tariff-plan-draws-debate-over-best-approach</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 21:05:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡车司机工会主席将在共和党大会上发表讲话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/teamsters-president-to-speak-at-republican-national-convention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布，卡车司机工会主席肖恩·奥布莱恩将于下个月在密尔沃基举行的共和党全国代表大会上发表讲话，此举可能会削弱总统乔·拜登对蓝领工会工人的吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/teamsters-president-to-speak-at-republican-national-convention</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
